	<MudTimelineItem Color="Color.Success" Size="Size.Large">
		<ItemOpposite>
			<MudText Color="Color.Success" Typo="Typo.h5">2014 - 2017</MudText>
		</ItemOpposite>
		<ItemContent>
			<MudText Color="Color.Success" Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">Business Academy Aarhus - Erhvervs akademi aarhus</MudText>
			<MudText>
				I got my degree in computer science with well above average grades.
				This was without a doubt my calling, and I loved it!
			</MudText>
		</ItemContent>
	</MudTimelineItem>

	<MudTimelineItem Color="Color.Info" Size="Size.Medium">
		<ItemOpposite>
			<MudText Color="Color.Info" Typo="Typo.h5">2009 - 2012</MudText>
		</ItemOpposite>
		<ItemContent>
			<MudText Color="Color.Info" Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">Danish Secondary school - HF VUC Aarhus</MudText>
			<MudText>
				I went to high school after having worked for some years, and got my high school diploma.
				I knew that i was aiming for computer science so I took the extra higher level mathematics class to prepare my grades for entry to the business academy.
			</MudText>
		</ItemContent>
	</MudTimelineItem>

	<MudTimelineItem Color="Color.Success" Size="Size.Small">
		<ItemOpposite>
			<MudText Color="Color.Success" Typo="Typo.h5">2000 - 2001</MudText>
		</ItemOpposite>
		<ItemContent>
			<MudText Color="Color.Success" Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">Danish IT Folk Highschool - IT-Højskolen Snoghøj</MudText>
			<MudText>
				I took a 6 months stay at a Danish folk high school which specialized in IT.
My main subject was networking and my finishing project was a web project.
Other courses during the semester was: 'IT and society', 'Basic life preparations' and 'The digital Denmark and abroad'.
At the end we had a 20 day trip to the US, driving up the west coast from San Fransisco, through LA and Las Vegas.
			</MudText>
		</ItemContent>
	</MudTimelineItem>

	<MudTimelineItem Color="Color.Info" Size="Size.Small">
		<ItemOpposite>
			<MudText Color="Color.Info" Typo="Typo.h5">1990 - 2000</MudText>
		</ItemOpposite>
		<ItemContent>
			<MudText Color="Color.Info" Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">Danish Primary school - Dansk Folkeskole</MudText>
			<MudText>
				I have passed 1st through 10th grade in the Danish school system.
				Here the 10th grade is not mandatory, but good to have as it prepares for secondary school.
			</MudText>
		</ItemContent>
